                   java.lang.String group,

                   java.lang.String facultyEmail,
                   java.lang.String room,
                   java.lang.String type,
                   int slotID)
        constructor for reservation class
        Parameters:
        Message - the message describing purpose for reservation
        group - the group(1,2,3,4) for which reservation is made.Blank Group refers to the whole audience of a course
        course - the course for which reservation is meant
        facultyEmail - the email of the instructor who teaches the course
        room - the room for which reservation is made
        type - lecture/lab/tutorial. Can be left blank as well
        slotID - the time slot in Integer
